---
// src/components/Hero.astro
// 针对“丽泽讲会”精神内核优化后的首屏
---
<section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-white pt-20">
   <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none">
       <div class="w-[600px] h-[600px] md:w-[800px] md:h-[800px] bg-gradient-to-tr from-cyan-100/40 to-blue-100/40 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-70 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
   </div>

   <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
       <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight">
           两泽<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00AEEF] to-blue-600">相丽</span>，<br class="md:hidden"/>智水<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-[#00AEEF]">共生</span>。
       </h1>

       <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-500 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed font-light">
           “君子以朋友讲习。”<br/>
           溯源婺学脉络，践行经世实学，打造平等交流的思想共同体。
       </p>

       <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-6">
           <a href="#dialogues" class="group px-8 py-4 bg-[#00AEEF] text-white rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#0099d3] transition-all shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/20 hover:shadow-cyan-500/40 hover:-translate-y-0.5 flex items-center">
               进入讲会
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
                 <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
               </svg>
           </a>
           <a href="/about" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-gray-600 border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-full font-semibold hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
               丽泽精神
           </a>
       </div>
   </div>
</section>